    <div class="intro-text">
        <strong>Pagination</strong> is a common UI pattern for handling large datasets.
        React-Bootstrap provides a full-featured <code>&lt;Pagination&gt;</code> component with
        <code>Item</code>, <code>First</code>, <code>Last</code>, <code>Previous</code>, and <code>Next</code> sub-components.
        <br/><br/>
        In this tutorial, we build a <strong>SimplePagination</strong> component that fetches user data,
        displays it in a table, and navigates pages using React-Bootstrap's pagination.
    </div>

